          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"success\":{\"type\":\"boolean\",\"description\":\"Was the question answered successfully? Does it include enough context to write great marketing copy for the business?\"},\"reasoning\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"Explain using the criteria why the question was or was not answered successfully.\"}},\"required\":[\"success\",\"reasoning\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n        # QA Evaluation Criteria\\n\\nALL answers must meet ALL four:\\n\\n1. **Specific** - Not vague (could describe 1000 businesses = fail)\\n2. **Actionable** - Can write marketing copy directly from it\\n3. **Authentic** - Their words, not marketing jargon (\\\"leverage synergies\\\" = fail)\\n4. **Insightful** - Shows understanding of business/audience\\n\\nClose but missing one element = NOT GREAT yet. Be critical but fair.\\n\\nOutput JSON: `{ success: boolean, reasoning: string }`\\n\\n        \\n        # QA: Business Idea\\n\\nLooking for:\\n1. What they do (not just industry)\\n2. Who it's for (even vague is OK here)\\n3. What makes it different (some hook/angle)\\n4. Why it matters (problem solved)\\n\\n**\\\"I'm still figuring it out\\\"** → success: true if directional enough\\n**Multiple ideas** → success: false, pick one\\n**Just industry name** (\\\"I'm in fitness\\\") → fail, need more\\n**Buzzword soup** → fail, need plain language\\n\\n        \\n        <current_topic>idea</current_topic>\\n        \\n        <user_answer>I like pasta.</user_answer>\\n        \\n        <existing_memory>No answer yet</existing_memory>\\n        \\n        <task>\\n        Evaluate if their answer is GREAT based on the criteria above.\\n        Output JSON: { \\\"success\\\": boolean, \\\"reasoning\\\": string }\\n        </task>\\n    \"}]}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1065,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1065,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01HNqgPKSg1Cd5usLmKkkQ4W\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01DVy6XKdaasEW7QBpwssChT\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"success\":false,\"reasoning\":\"The answer \\\"I like pasta\\\" fails on all four criteria. It's not specific (liking pasta doesn't describe a business), not actionable (can't write marketing copy from a personal preference), not authentic in a business context (it's a personal statement, not a business idea), and not insightful (shows no understanding of a business model, target audience, differentiation, or problem being solved). This is a personal preference, not a business idea. We need: What do they actually DO with pasta? Who would they serve? What's their angle? What problem does it solve?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1083,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":171,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
